据马特·格勒宁透露，许多人都把《恐惧角》列入心目中的十佳剧集<ref name="groening" />。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》曾于2003年评选史上最优秀的25集《辛普森一家》，本集排名第三<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2003/02/02/best-simpsons-episodes-nos-1-5 | title = The Family Dynamic | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | date = 2003-02-02 | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archivedate = 2016-02-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160225141336/http://www.ew.com/article/2003/02/02/best-simpsons-episodes-nos-1-5}}</ref>。同年，《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》在庆祝电视剧第300集《[[巴特的讨价还价|巴特的讨价还价]]》（{{lang|en|''Barting Over''}}）播出之际发文，登出[[辛普森一家档案馆|辛普森一家档案馆]]网站评选的十佳剧集，《恐惧角》名列第九<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160413053107/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2003-02-06-fan-favorites_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2003-02-06-fan-favorites_x.htm | title = 10 fan favorites | accessdate = 2016-09-18 | last = Paakkinen | first = Jouni | date = 2003-02-06 | work = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | archivedate = 2016-04-13}}</ref>。2006年，{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}把这集评为《辛普森一家》第五季最佳剧集<ref name="IGN2">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411221945/http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/01/08/the-simpsons-20-seasons-20-episodes | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/01/08/the-simpsons-20-seasons-20-episodes | title = The Simpsons: 17 Seasons, 17 Episodes | last1 = Goldman | first1 = Eric | author2 = Dan Iverson | author3 = Brian Zoromski | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2006-09-08 | accessdate = 2015-12-14 | archivedate = 2016-04-11}}</ref>。2007年，《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》又将《恐惧角》评为《辛普森一家》中第四优秀的剧集，称赞节目无论是在恶搞其他电影还是常设角色发展方面都有几乎无与伦比的大师级表现<ref>{{cite web | first = John | last = Orvted | title = The Simpsons: Springfield's Best | work = [[名利场_(杂志)|Vanity Fair]] | date = 2007-07-05 | archivedate = 2016-07-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160713083131/http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2007/08/top10simpsons200708 | url = http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2007/08/top10simpsons200708 | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2007年，《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的詹姆斯·沃尔顿（{{lang|en|James Walton}}）把本集列入《辛普森一家》十佳剧集<ref>{{cite news | last = Walton | first = James | title = The 10 Best Simpsons TV Episodes (In Chronological Order) | newspaper = [[每日电讯报|The Telegraph]] | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/8791597/The-10-best-Simpsons-TV-episodes.html | page = 3 | date = 2007-07-21 | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | archivedate = 2016-08-01 | deadurl = no | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801192517/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/8791597/The-10-best-Simpsons-TV-episodes.html}}</ref>，《[[太阳先驱报|太阳先驱报]]》（{{lang|en|''Herald Sun''}}）也于同年将其评为《辛普森一家》最优秀的20集之一<ref>{{cite news | title = The Simpsons Top 20 | work = Herald Sun | date = 2007-04-21 | page = W09}}</ref>。2008年，瑞典《[[布罗斯报|布罗斯报]]》（{{lang|sw|Borås Tidning}}）的卡尔·阿克斯通（{{lang|sw|Karl Åkerström}}）称《恐惧角》是他眼中最优秀的《辛普森一家》剧集<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bt.se/karl-akerstrom/topp-tio-1991/#article-toolbar-bottom | title = Topp Tio 1991 | last = Åkerström | first = Karl | date = 2008-09-29 | newspaper = Borås Tidning | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | archivedate = 2016-01-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110104750/http://www.bt.se/karl-akerstrom/topp-tio-1991/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2010年，迈克尔·莫兰（{{lang|en|Michael Moran}}）在《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》发文，称《恐惧角》可以在《辛普森一家》历史上所有剧集中排名第四，同2007年《[[偏锋杂志|偏锋杂志]]》的托德·范德韦尔夫（{{lang|en|Todd VanDerWerff}}）排位相同<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/arts/tv-radio/article2448600.ece | title = The 10 best Simpsons episodes ever | last = Moran | first = Michael | date = 2010-01-14 | newspaper = [[泰晤士报|The Times]] | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | archive-date = 2016-01-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110104750/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/arts/tv-radio/article2448600.ece | dead-url = no }}{{subscription required}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 5 for the Day: The Simpsons | work = Slant Magazine | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | date = 2007-08-01 | last = VanDerWerff | first = Todd | archivedate = 2016-05-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160531180327/http://www.slantmagazine.com/house/article/5-for-the-day-the-simpsons | url = http://www.slantmagazine.com/house/article/5-for-the-day-the-simpsons | deadurl = no}}</ref>。此外，《辛普森一家》的配音演员[[汉克·阿扎里亚|汉克·阿扎里亚]]也称这集是他在节目中最喜欢的剧集<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-04-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160401193040/https://twitter.com/hankazaria/status/293843041003921408 | deadurl = no | url = https://twitter.com/HankAzaria/status/293843041003921408 | title = Hank Azaria Twitter status 3:10 PM 22 Jan 13 | last = Azaria | first = Hank | date = 2013-01-22 | work = Twitter | accessdate = 2016-04-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307232259/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/09/hank-azarias-favorite-simpsons-voice-video_n_3729696.html?ncid=edlinkusaolp00000003 | title = Hank Azaria Shares Favorite 'Simpsons' Voice And Episode On 'Watch What Happens: Live' (VIDEO) | date = 2013-08-09 | newspaper = [[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]] | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/09/hank-azarias-favorite-simpsons-voice-video_n_3729696.html?ncid=edlinkusaolp00000003 | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

{{lang|en|IGN}}网站的罗伯特·坎宁（{{lang|en|Robert Canning}}）给予本集十分的高度评价（最高十分），称这是《辛普森一家》中杂耍家鲍伯出场的最佳剧集。他还称，节目的出众虽然通过多个方面表现出来，但最令他印象深刻的就是鲍伯在节目中的野蛮和专注程度。他一心要杀死巴特，除欺骗假释委员会外根本没有试图隐瞒。相比之下，之前出场的鲍伯要优柔寡断得多。这正是鲍伯的全盛时期，一心复仇、光芒四射而又令人捧腹的全盛时期。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/06/30/the-simpsons-flashback-cape-feare-review | title = The Simpsons Flashback: "Cape Feare" Review | last = Canning | first = Robert | date = 2009-06-30 | publisher = IGN | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110104749/http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/06/30/the-simpsons-flashback-cape-feare-review | archivedate = 2016-01-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。此后，坎宁又在评选杂耍家鲍伯十佳剧集时再度把《恐惧角》排在首位<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/12/03/the-simpsons-top-10-sideshow-bob-episodes?page=2 | title = The Simpsons: Top 10 Sideshow Bob Episodes (Page 2) | last = Canning | first = Robert | date = 2009-12-02 | publisher = IGN | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | archivedate = 2016-01-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110104749/http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/12/03/the-simpsons-top-10-sideshow-bob-episodes?page=2}}</ref>。《[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]》内森·拉宾（{{lang|en|Nathan Rabin}}）指出，节目中为了延长时间而加入的内容堪称《辛普森一家》历史上最犀利、最搞笑而且最古怪的噱头，不但突破节目本身的限制，而且这段犁耙戏码很可能是这集对喜剧最大的贡献，其优点还远远不止于止。杂耍家鲍伯出场的剧集一直身处《辛普森一家》的最佳之列，《恐惧角》则代表今后所有杂耍家鲍伯剧集应力求看齐的金牌标准<ref>{{cite web | publisher = ''The A.V. Club'' | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | url = http://www.avclub.com/tvclub/the-simpsons-classic-cape-feare-88667 | title = The Simpsons (Classic): "Cape Feare" | last = Rabin | first = Nathan | date = 2012-11-18 | archivedate = 2016-01-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110104749/http://www.avclub.com/tvclub/the-simpsons-classic-cape-feare-88667}}</ref>。《[[帝国杂志|帝国]]》将鲍伯把自己绑在辛普森家族车下后遭遇的事故评为《辛普森一家》最佳电影恶搞情节第八位<ref>{{cite journal | author = Colin Kennedy | date = 2004-09 | title = The Ten Best Movie Gags In ''The Simpsons'' | journal = ''[[帝国杂志|Empire]]'' | page = 77}}</ref>。《[[全面电影|全面电影]]》（{{lang|en|''Total Film''}}）则把本集对《恐怖角》的戏仿评为《辛普森一家》历史上最佳电影指涉的第33名<ref name="totalfilm" />。挪威的《[[经理报|经理报]]》（{{lang|no|Nettavisen}}）还把杂耍家鲍伯的纹身“死吧巴特，去死吧”评为电影和电视史上所有纹身的第五位<ref>{{cite news | url = http://pub.nettavisen.no/1367489.html | title = De beste film-tatoveringene | date = 2007-10-06 | newspaper = Nettavisen | page = 2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110104751/http://pub.nettavisen.no/1367489.html | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | archivedate = 2016-01-10 }}</ref>。

2012年，美国剧作家[[安妮·沃什伯恩|安妮·沃什伯恩]]（{{lang|en|Anne Washburn}}）的剧作《[[伯恩斯先生，后电子时代剧作|伯恩斯先生，后电子时代剧作]]》（{{lang|en|''Mr. Burns, a Post-Electric Play''}}）面世，这部剧作就是根据《恐惧角》改编，电视剧的剧情还是剧作的重要组成部分<ref>{{cite web | last1 = Del Signore | first1 = John | title = Excellent: Playwright Anne Washburn Talks ''Mr. Burns, A Post-Electric Play'' | url = http://gothamist.com/2013/09/27/anne_washburn.php | website = ''Gothamist'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150509152002/http://gothamist.com/2013/09/27/anne_washburn.php | publisher = Gothamist LLC | accessdate = 2016-09-17 | date = 2013-09-27 | archivedate = 2015-05-09 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

